{"tid":1953942,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"切勿把批鬥當成習慣","createTime":"2020-04-01T12:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T13:07:17.000Z","uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"deac8fff763690bff68cb904671e11fea2d6ebef","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"都講左好多次，我地本錢唔多，冇後盾，冇大台。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />從來光復香港都只係你一個人嘅時代革命，大家要做係揾同路人，擴大自己嘅陣營，而唔係去屌人偽黃，做得唔夠多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n一個社運嘅失敗，係因為分化、批鬥，大家有眼見，對歷史有啲了解嘅都會知到。你地要明白，即使人地做得比你少，人地都有努力，比啲鼓勵人啦好冇？一句加油係微不足道，但香港人加油除左係口號，都係我地嘅動力。多啲鼓勵其他人啊，同咁多位區議員、手足講句多謝啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家都知中共最鍾意做嘅就係滲透、分化、派五毛網軍，大家醒目啲啦，中共就嚟被天滅，但一樣有人做嘢㗎。</span></span>而且藍屍狗愈嚟愈團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，睇翻我地好似成盤散沙咁啊，班藍屍狗都有進步到喇，無論係YouTube戰線、文宣、起底。我知大家都好嬲，會嬲黑警保護班藍屍狗，但大家嬲嘅同時，要揾新出路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真呢場運動去到咁耐，一定會有樽頸位，係我個人嘅角度，悼念就會有手足被捕，因為個場玩到爛曬有曬plan，我自己都有諗過咁做係好定唔好，不妨你哋自己都諗吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不公義係事實，唔係話忘記，但你比人ss一次，會有更多嘅事延伸出嚟。</span></span>咁樣嘅時候，我地需要突破，例如我屋企人會係排隊買嘢嘅時候同啲師奶吹水，再少少少少咁教下佢地咁，又會考下佢地咩人好咩人差。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後:<br />\n咁多位手足，好多謝你地堅持左咁耐，大家都失落過、憤怒過、開心過，希望大家唔好放棄，都唔好忘記，我知道真香港人係唔會忘記任何一件事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近愈嚟愈多上門拘捕，我希望咁多位萬事小心，唔好單獨行事，小心跟尾狗，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特別係呢兩個月</span></span>。<br />\n我地冇本錢，呢個時間唔應該再批鬥，不如大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">多啲睇黃channel，打下twitter戰線，做下文宣，簽下聯署。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">多謝咁多位手足，be water my friends</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c97133f2a3aa707d64e2174b61786f4a5f15f3","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bc92a63351e868b8d78f87b81add4ec9f4c9ad","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4760a4c65e3950514fbd7620351ad94961b46d5","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4681739545f13da0cb69f5b7abe6174b6c2ba2ba","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de899971af816579fa8c77553793de957bf9604a","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3d7a0ab30ca9d24660b11e436d735b5d720f88","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:58:32.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac3482fb3a9bf1ef1833ca1860609a901370608","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f36554b296b0bd6b7fcc9fde322f1da69ce6aa1","tid":1953942,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:58:5